title: 125 Days, 750,000 Uses, One Realization: Some of Our AI Agents Are Now Truly Part of the Team. Replit v3 Was The First
summary: The other day I presented at Replit on 125 days of building 10+ production apps through vibe coding. Apps that have now been used over 750,000 times. I went in thinking I’d share what I’d learned. I came out with something bigger. The Replit AI agent isn’t a tool anymore. It’s part of my team. ... Continue Reading
